content:
Launch OmniScripts in Communities from URLs

To add the Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper component to a Community page:

On a Community Builder page, click on the Components tab.
Search for the Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper component, and drag it onto the page.
Leave the fields in the component blank.

In the LWC OmniScript Name field, enter the component name of your OmniScript with the prefix c:. The OmniScript's component name is a combination of the Type, SubType, and Language of your OmniScript without spaces.

Configure URL to Access Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper Component

Launch any LWC OmniScript on a Community Page by sending a URL to the Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper component on the page.

To test an OmniScript using the LWC OmniScript Wrapper in the Community Builder:

Check the Stand Alone Mode checkbox.
Enter the component name of your OmniScript with the prefix c:.
title: Launching OmniScripts in Communities
